Question 10
Develop a program to check student grades based on marks using a loop.

ANSWER
<?php
$marks = 90;
echo "Student Marks: $marks%<br>";
if ($marks >= 75) {
    echo "Grade: First Class";
} elseif ($marks >= 60 && $marks <= 74) {
    echo "Grade: Second Class";
} elseif ($marks >= 40 && $marks <= 59) {
    echo "Grade: Third Class";
} else {
    echo "Grade: Fail";
}
?>


OUTPUT
Student Marks: 90%
Grade: First Class

